graph LR
    Plan[Execution plan<br/>join_strategy = genie_route<br/>genie_route_plan per space] --> GenieAgent[SQL Synthesis Genie Agent]
    GenieAgent --> Build[Create tools only for relevant Genie spaces]
    Build --> Mode{Execution mode}

    Mode -->|LangGraph agent mode| ToolCalls[Tool calling orchestration]
    Mode -->|RunnableParallel mode| Parallel[Parallel Genie invocation]

    ToolCalls --> GenieTools[Genie agents as tools<br/>question per space]
    Parallel --> GenieTools
    GenieTools --> Outputs[Per-space answers<br/>optional SQL + reasoning]
    Outputs --> Merge[Merge routed outputs]
    Merge --> Final[Combined SQL synthesis result<br/>for downstream execution]

    classDef agentClass fill:#4A90E2,stroke:#2E5C8A,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef dataClass fill:#50C878,stroke:#2E7D4E,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef processClass fill:#F5A623,stroke:#C17D11,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef decisionClass fill:#8E44AD,stroke:#6C3483,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    class GenieAgent agentClass
    class Plan,Outputs,Final dataClass
    class Build,ToolCalls,Parallel,GenieTools,Merge processClass
    class Mode decisionClass
